reviews.text:
Hong Kong Style? Western restaurant~
It places very near the gate of Shau Kei Wan Plaza shopping mall. 
The restaurant is small but the host and staffs are very kind. So we feel convenient😊 
We ordered bolognese pasta, omelette&pork cutlet set, hamburger steak&spicy sausage set, chicken burger and duo cheese potato. 
Tomato sauce is sweet a little. But all dishes are not salty or oily, so my family enjoyed the time~
I am sorry that restaurant is far from my home..I want to have its dishes everyday^^
We will visit again soon~

result.name: Smiling Shaukeiwan Plaza

reviews.text: A slightly old mall with no restaurants (I'm not sure). I don't come here often. ☹️
If you have much time you can go and walk around. Not many things to shop.

To those who seek old timey figures, handhelds, model cars, etc., there is a new-ish store opened on the 2nd floor(the top floor) that sell all these and more. There are just mountain of old but still in the box figures and such. Worth a visit to find your childhood memory.
A small shopping mall
There is something attractively eerie about this place. It looks as if it has not changed since the 1980s, but that is part of its charm.
